color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Automation of Operations:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Automate crucial retail tasks such as stock deduction upon purchase, invoice generation, and status tracking, thereby minimizing human effort and errors.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
