color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Equip the administration with a comprehensive dashboard featuring visual analytics, allowing for informed decision-making regarding inventory and sales strategies.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >1.3 Scope of the Project</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >The scope of the Digital Mobile Store encapsulates a wide array of features designed to cover the entire lifecycle of an e-commerce transaction:</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
