color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Registration, secure login, profile updates, and order history tracking for customers.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
