color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;An AJAX-powered shopping cart that checks stock availability in real-time, preventing over-ordering. The checkout supports both Online Payment processing and Cash on Delivery (COD).</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
