font-weight:bold;font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >1.4 Existing System</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >In today's highly competitive retail environment, managing a mobile store manually presents significant challenges. The existing system primarily relies on physical ledgers or basic spreadsheet software. Operations such as tracking inventory, recording daily sales, and managing customer feedback are disjointed and labor-intensive.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Specific pain points of the existing manual system include:</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Geographical Constraints:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;The store can only serve customers who physically visit the location during operational hours.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Inventory Errors:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Manual tracking often leads to stock discrepancies, where items are either over-ordered or surprisingly out of stock when a customer requests them.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Poor Customer Engagement:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;There is no centralized mechanism for customers to leave reviews or for the store to showcase its best-selling items effectively.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Inefficient Sales Tracking:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Calculating monthly revenue and identifying top-selling products requires manual auditing of physical receipts.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >1.5 Proposed System</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >The proposed </span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >phoneKART</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;system is engineered to overcome the inefficiencies of the manual retail model. By deploying a centralized, web-based platform, the system entirely automates the sales and inventory management workflow.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >The proposed solution provides a synchronized database where every purchase instantly updates the stock levels. It offers a 24/7 digital storefront, dramatically expanding the business's reach. Administrators gain a bird's-eye view of operations through the dashboard, drastically reducing administrative overhead. The integration of modern web technologies ensures the platform is fast, secure, and highly scalable, laying a strong foundation for future growth.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >1.6 Platform Used (Hardware & Software)</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >The application is built using a modern, industry-standard technology stack to ensure high performance and maintainability.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Software Specifications:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
