color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Observation & Competitor Analysis:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Studied leading e-commerce platforms (like Amazon and Flipkart) to identify industry-standard features that users expect, such as AJAX carts, rich product galleries, and intuitive checkout flows.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >2.3 Problem in Existing System</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >The requirement gathering phase exposed several critical flaws in the existing manual business model:</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >High Manpower Requirement:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Staff is required to physically manage stock displays, answer repetitive customer inquiries, and manually process every transaction.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Time-Consuming:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Customers spend a significant amount of time traveling to the store, browsing physical items, and waiting in line for billing.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Data Loss & Paperwork:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Reliance on physical paper receipts and ledgers makes the business vulnerable to data loss and makes long-term sales analysis nearly impossible.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Lack of Scalability:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;A physical store has a hard limit on how many customers it can serve simultaneously; a digital store has virtually no such limit.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >2.4 Conclusion</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >The requirement analysis distinctly justified the need for the </span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >phoneKART</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;web application. By transitioning to a web-based Laravel system, the business can automate inventory, streamline the checkout process, and provide a superior, 24/7 service to a much broader audience. The documented requirements laid the groundwork for the logical and physical design phases, ensuring all operational needs were met.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h1 style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:24.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:22.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >Chapter-3: Logical Design</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;font-weight:bold;
text-transform:uppercase;font-size:24.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:22.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h1><h2 style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >3.1 Introduction</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >The logical design phase formulates the conceptual blueprint of the phoneKART system. It utilizes standardized modeling diagrams to visualize data flow, entity relationships, and user interactions. This abstraction ensures the development team has a clear, graphical understanding of the system's architecture before writing any code.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >3.2 DFD (0th, 1st, 2nd level)</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;font-weight:bold;
font-size:18.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >The Data Flow Diagram maps how information circulates within the e-commerce system, from user inputs (like registration and checkout) to database storage and output generation (like invoices and reports).</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
