color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >The Use Case Diagram depicts the system from the users' perspective. It outlines the distinct actions available to the "Customer" (Browse, Add to Cart, Checkout, Review) and the "Administrator" (Manage Inventory, View Reports, Process Orders).</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
