color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >The application is modularized using Laravel's MVC architecture. The major modules include:</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo9;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Authentication Module:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Handles user registration, secure login, password hashing, and role-based access control (RBAC). It includes custom middleware to restrict Admin routes.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo9;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Storefront & Cart Module:</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;Manages the public-facing product grids, individual product detail pages, and an AJAX-driven shopping cart that stores items in the database (or session) and validates stock dynamically.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=justify  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.8000pt;margin-left:12.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo9;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(0,0,0);
font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;
